  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This synthetic adversarial sample embeds W-AR-02: the decision record records Accepted while one or more CredibilityFactor objects report achievedLevel strictly below requiredLevel, constituting a rebutting defeater of the acceptance decision.",
