      "rationale": "The CFD solver is under version control and a regression suite exists covering laminar and turbulent benchmark cases. Change-control documentation is partially complete; formal sign-off records for the hemolysis-specific sub-models are pending final review. The assessment team considers the overall software quality posture adequate for engineering purposes given the Monte Carlo UQ envelope applied downstream."
